1060
01:12:43,721 --> 01:12:46,057
No, no, no.
It's just a shirt, okay?

1061
01:12:46,141 --> 01:12:49,603
The one that he wears all the
time is about to fall apart

1062
01:12:49,687 --> 01:12:51,522
and I thought that--
A shirt?

1063
01:12:51,606 --> 01:12:54,776
No, I don't think there will be
