that he gets that?

1067
01:13:01,076 --> 01:13:03,579
Sure. We'll send it to him.

1068
01:13:24,521 --> 01:13:26,065
Maybe they missed the flight.
I hope not.

1069
01:13:28,860 --> 01:13:31,613
There... there they are!
