1070
01:13:43,628 --> 01:13:46,131
Oh, yeah! Oh!
Grandpa!

1071
01:13:46,214 --> 01:13:47,299
Hello.
 : We missed you so much.

1072
01:13:47,383 --> 01:13:48,217
We missed you too.

1073
01:13:48,300 --> 01:13:51,012
Lots of stories to tell you.

1074
01:13:51,095 --> 01:13:53,307
I can't see you any bigger,

1075
01:13:53,390 --> 01:13:57,311
