Three and half pounds!

1076
01:13:59,773 --> 01:14:01,942
They lost our bags.

1077
01:14:01,984 --> 01:14:03,110
Hi.
Hi.

1078
01:14:03,152 --> 01:14:05,488
Hi, Nicholas.
Hi, Nicole.

1079
01:14:07,073 --> 01:14:11,120
Thanks for coming, Dad.

1080
01:14:11,204 --> 01:14:12,539
I missed you more.

1081
01:14:12,622 --> 01:14:15,250
They lost our bags.
That's why we were so late.

1082
01:14:15,334 --> 01:14:16,919
Let's go.

1083
01:14:21,132 --> 01:14:22,634
You go to my place

1084
01:14:22,718 --> 01:14:24,637
or yours?
I guess it'll be better

1085
01:14:24,720 --> 01:14:27,432
