All right, then.

1086
01:14:31,312 --> 01:14:32,855
I love you, Julie.

1087
01:14:32,939 --> 01:14:35,650
You saved our son.
It wasn't me.

1088
01:14:35,734 --> 01:14:37,736
It was Alexy who saved him.

1089
01:14:37,820 --> 01:14:39,447
Well, then, I love him too.

1090
01:14:41,950 --> 01:14:44,745
Dad looks terrible.

1091
01:14:44,828 --> 01:14:47,999
His beloved Bogusha dumped
him. Met some other Polish guy.

1092
01:14:48,041 --> 01:14:49,793
A bit younger, I gather.
 

1093
01:14:51,336 --> 01:14:55,174
Dad, you have to open the door
to get through it.

1094
01:15:04,144 --> 01:15:05,520
Honey, what are you doing?

1095
01:15:05,562 --> 01:15:08,107
I check myself in the mirror
every night

1096
01:15:08,190 --> 01:15:10,693
