I don't catch cancer.

1097
01:15:10,777 --> 01:15:14,990
You can't catch cancer.
It's not a contagious disease.

1098
01:15:15,074 --> 01:15:16,701
But we're twins.
Doesn't matter.

1099
01:15:16,784 --> 01:15:18,453
You're separate people.

1100
01:15:18,536 --> 01:15:21,999
And anyway, you can't catch something
that's gone. It doesn't exist.

1101
01:15:22,082 --> 01:15:23,292
Nicholas isn't sick anymore.

1102
01:15:23,376 --> 01:15:24,878
You understand?

1103
01:15:24,961 --> 01:15:26,421
Yeah.

1104
01:15:29,800 --> 01:15:32,595
Tonight, can you put Nicholas's
bed right next to mine

1105
01:15:32,679 --> 01:15:34,640
