with Nicholas.

1108
01:15:44,485 --> 01:15:45,445
Okay.

1109
01:15:47,656 --> 01:15:50,826
What's it gonna be? Ah!
 

1110
01:15:54,247 --> 01:15:56,249
So how was it?
It was great.

1111
01:15:56,291 --> 01:15:58,586
