1112
01:15:58,627 --> 01:16:00,755
The healer.
Alexy?

1113
01:16:00,797 --> 01:16:02,299
Yes, Alexy.

1114
01:16:02,382 --> 01:16:05,803
How many times did you see him?
Hundreds of times.

1115
01:16:05,886 --> 01:16:09,307
