All the time.

1122
01:16:26,537 --> 01:16:29,165
Like what kind of dates?
What did they do?

1123
01:16:29,248 --> 01:16:31,209
He can do anything he wants.

1124
01:16:31,293 --> 01:16:34,171
Once, he brung this man
who weighed over 400 pounds,

1125
01:16:34,213 --> 01:16:37,425
and lifted him over his head
with one hand. Like this.

1126
01:16:39,970 --> 01:16:41,680
But what did he do to you?

1127
01:16:49,857 --> 01:16:51,359
His hands were hot.

1128
01:16:53,028 --> 01:16:56,866
And he never gave you nothing?
He never gave you any...

1129
01:16:56,949 --> 01:16:58,201
any, like, pills or...

1130
01:16:58,284 --> 01:17:01,413
herbs or... nothing?

1131
01:17:01,496 --> 01:17:05,501
I want to send a video on how
to play baseball to Piotr, okay?

1132
01:17:05,585 --> 01:17:07,420
Yeah, we can do that.

1133
01:17:52,392 --> 01:17:54,145
I missed you so much, Julie.

1134
01:17:57,941 --> 01:17:59,484
Do you know that?

1135
01:18:34,444 --> 01:18:35,946
Come back to me.

1136
01:18:35,988 --> 01:18:39,117
You're gonna have to give me
some time to get used to all this.

1137
01:18:43,330 --> 01:18:44,832
You smell different.

1138
01:18:47,836 --> 01:18:50,506
There's something different
about you. I can feel it.

1139
01:19:01,352 --> 01:19:03,146
It's him, isn't it?

1140
01:19:06,734 --> 01:19:09,779
I don't... I don't even know
how to describe it.

1141
01:19:11,698 --> 01:19:14,243
It's so... different.

1142
01:19:14,327 --> 01:19:16,454
It's... it's unreal.

1143
01:19:18,623 --> 01:19:22,545
I don't even know if he's...
interested in our world,

1144
01:19:22,628 --> 01:19:24,422
