of spontaneous remission.

1151
01:20:35,844 --> 01:20:38,597
Are you sure the Russian man
only touched him?

1152
01:20:38,639 --> 01:20:39,556
No tumour.

1153
01:20:50,695 --> 01:20:52,656
Dad!

1154
01:20:55,785 --> 01:20:57,245
Dad!

1155
01:21:03,836 --> 01:21:05,797
Dad, what is going on?

1156
01:21:05,880 --> 01:21:08,342
