1157
01:21:11,220 --> 01:21:12,681
Why'd you throw it back?

1158
01:21:12,722 --> 01:21:16,185
I didn't like her face.
Stupid snout.

1159
01:21:18,020 --> 01:21:20,023
You okay?

1160
01:21:22,109 --> 01:21:24,028
I'm... okay.

1161
01:21:24,070 --> 01:21:26,364
I just drunk... too much.

1162
01:21:26,406 --> 01:21:30,202
You were right. This Bogusha,

1163
01:21:30,244 --> 01:21:32,705
