1164
01:21:34,708 --> 01:21:37,836
But she did me good.

1165
01:21:37,920 --> 01:21:39,881
She...

1166
01:21:39,922 --> 01:21:42,133
made him stand up.

1167
01:21:45,221 --> 01:21:47,348
And she saved Nick.

1168
01:21:49,351 --> 01:21:53,564
So, you know,
everything makes sense.

1169
01:21:58,946 --> 01:22:00,740
 

1170
01:23:12,828 --> 01:23:16,082
 

1171
01:24:38,893 --> 01:24:40,770
 

