01:24:47,361 --> 01:24:48,821
Hello?

1173
01:24:54,287 --> 01:24:55,788
Alexy.

1174
01:24:58,959 --> 01:25:01,837
I know that it's you.
I can hear your breath.

1175
01:25:01,921 --> 01:25:03,381
Say something.

1176
01:25:04,925 --> 01:25:06,051
Say anything.

1177
01:25:06,134 --> 01:25:07,595
Where are you?

1178
01:25:09,138 --> 01:25:11,224
Are you still there?

1179
01:25:15,062 --> 01:25:18,274
Please, just...
just tell me what to do.

1180
01:25:18,316 --> 01:25:21,528
I'll do whatever
you want me to do.

1181
01:25:21,612 --> 01:25:22,780
Where are--
 

1182
01:25:47,394 --> 01:25:48,854
We can't go on like this.

1183
01:25:52,567 --> 01:25:54,944
I'm just gonna take the kids
and go to my sister's.

1184
01:25:57,239 --> 01:25:59,450
Henry...

1185
01:25:59,533 --> 01:26:01,411
I don't... know--

1186
01:26:01,494 --> 01:26:02,913
You shouldn't
say anything yet.

1187
01:26:02,996 --> 01:26:04,999
Just take your time
and think about it.

1188
01:26:05,040 --> 01:26:06,542
And I will do the same.

1189
01:26:10,881 --> 01:26:12,007
Ah, Julie,

1190
01:26:12,049 --> 01:26:14,010
I love you so much.

1191
01:26:14,051 --> 01:26:15,219
I know.

1192
01:26:18,765 --> 01:26:20,685
