1194
01:26:22,562 --> 01:26:24,147
What do you want me to say?

1195
01:26:24,231 --> 01:26:26,233
No, I'm not talking
about my affair.

1196
01:26:33,408 --> 01:26:36,245
I feel I've disappointed you
in a...

1197
01:26:36,287 --> 01:26:37,747
global sense.

1198
01:26:41,627 --> 01:26:43,004
Say something.

1199
01:26:45,298 --> 01:26:47,467
We've been through
a very difficult period.

1200
01:26:47,551 --> 01:26:49,428
